data.description: Nestled in the highly sought-after Spanos Park community, this beautiful home offers an ideal blend of comfort and convenience offering a quiet and convenient lifestyle. Situated in a peaceful neighborhood with easy access to major shopping centers and a short drive to the 99 freeway, this residence is move-in ready. The house features a downstairs bedroom for added convenience and a spacious backyard with a pool, providing a perfect space for relaxation. Large walk in master closet with separate shower, bath and restroom. The appeal of the home is complemented by sharing its back fence with a 180-acre park situated in a beautiful oak-forest setting, that you can enjoy views from your master bedroom adding to the overall tranquility of the area. In essence, this home in Spanos Park is a comfortable and accessible choice, making it an attractive option for those seeking a relaxed living experience in a well-established community.
